ENUS:
Planet tweaks:
    Four new minerals, Sulfur, Aluminum, Tungsten, and Radiolite, minerals can now be generated underwater;
    Added atmosphere types to the vast majority of Earth-like planets, and the ability to use Atmospheric Harvesting Stations for resource harvesting;
    New seawater oceans, hydrochloric acid oceans, and nitric acid oceans;
    Planetary Coordination Center, with the freedom to choose from a wide range of coordinated gains for your factories.
Production tweaks:
    New mineral-related materials and recipes;
    Chemical recipe expansion, three different plastics with different properties for different production needs;
    Mineral Processing Technology, allowing minerals to be pre-treated for increased output or for use in fuel cells;
    Addition of multiple fuel rods for Icarus' interstellar expansion;
    Construction recipe requirement adjustments, consolidating common requirements into mechanical components to increase production line efficiency;
    Production overflow mechanic, allowing byproduct overflow to ensure production continuity (adjustable in settings).
Building tweaks:
    Manufacturing table split into three different precision manufacturing types, which are not generalizable;
    Enhancements to automated production attributes such as power supply range, conveyor belts, sorter speed, and manufacturing table speed;
    Atmospheric collection stations and orbital collectors no longer consume power, allowing oil wells and large mining machines to be built over water;
    Power generation power adjusted so that power = building base power * fuel bonus;
    Fuel cell power plants can only operate in oxygenated atmospheres (except fuel rods); fission power stations, isotope temperature difference generators added;
    Black Mist building tweak; Black Mist Fabrication Stations allow for the creation of most recipes, while Black Mist Furnaces double the output of items;
    Mega Buildings: manufacturing centers that use conveyor belts to transfer raw materials and products far more efficiently than normal facilities;
    Material Decomposition Facility, which converts items into sand and earth, and can also dismantle buildings for manufacturing materials.
Technology tweaks:
    Technology Exploration Mode to hide technologies that cannot be developed at the moment (can be adjusted in Settings);
    Add multiple composite matrices and corresponding research requirements;
    Construct Quantum Boxes to instantly transport items across galaxies; consume Negentropic Singularity to perform Remote Folding; use Global Shield Energy to broadcast.
Weapon tweaks:
    Produce tungsten warheads, nuclear missiles;
    Construction of UV laser towers, electromagnetic cannons;
    Use antimatter leaping missiles for transplanetary support.
Other tweaks:
    Mech fuel silos can only be powered using fuel rods;
    Quick start mode to get every adventure underway quickly;
    A self-contained quantization calculator to aid in building production lines.
